<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.8">
<l>uṇpatu colli lulakaḷantāṉ vāyamutaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇpaṭai koḷḷiṟ kaṭalvaṇṇaṉ kaittalattē</l>
<l>peṇpaṭaiyā ruṉmēṟ perumpūcal cāṟṟukiṉṟār</l>
<l>paṇpala ceykiṉṟāy pāñca caṉṉiyamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [we] speak of what [you] eat: [it is] the nectar from the lips of</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who measured the worlds!</l>
<l>If [we] consider [your] bed: [it is] the palm of the ocean-hued [Lord]!</l>
<l>Legions of women are clamouring against you!</l>
<l>You are doing discourteous things, O Pañcajanya!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
